OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family demand
OL,4,Canswers as they visit the UK for the
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,FWords by ITV News Senior Producer Cat
OL,8,FDinneny
OL,10,FThe family of a woman who was killed
OL,11,Fand dumped in a car boot have
OL,12,Ftravelled to the UK for the first time
OL,13,Fto demand justice for their daughter.
OL,15,FHarshita Brella was allegedly murdered
OL,16,Fby her husband, Pankaj Lamba, before
OL,17,Fhe bundled her into the boot of his
OL,18,Fcar and fled to India. He is still on
OL,19,Fthe run, 18 months later.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778926014
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family demand
OL,4,Canswers as they visit the UK for the
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,FNow, ITV News has followed Harshita's
OL,8,Ffamily from their home in New Delhi to
OL,9,FCorby, as they search for answers. It
OL,10,Fis the first time they have made the
OL,11,F4,000-mile trip.
OL,13,FSpeaking to ITV News as they prepared
OL,14,Fto leave India, Harshita's sister,
OL,15,FSonia Dabas, said: "Her pain, strength
OL,16,Fand memories are inside me, and I'm
OL,17,Fgoing to get justice for my sister."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778926014
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family demand
OL,4,Canswers as they visit the UK for the
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,FHarshita and Lamba had an arranged
OL,8,Fmarriage in India in August 2023 and
OL,9,Fmoved to the UK in the spring of the
OL,10,Ffollowing year.
OL,12,FITV News understands that Lamba was in
OL,13,Fthe UK on a student visa and Harshita,
OL,14,Fwho was 24, started working in a
OL,15,Fdistribution centre in Corby.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778926014
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family demand
OL,4,Canswers as they visit the UK for the
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,FSpeaking through an interpreter,
OL,8,FHarshita's mother, Sudesh Kumari,
OL,9,Fsaid: "Whenever she would call, she
OL,10,Fwould say she is fine and happy and
OL,11,Fenjoying life. She would say to me,
OL,12,F'Mummy, I will bring you over here, my
OL,13,Flife is happy, I will bring you when I
OL,14,Fhave some money and my own house'.
OL,16,F"I never anticipated that I would have
OL,17,Fto travel to Corby under these tragic
OL,18,Fcircumstances. I feel so sad about
OL,19,Fcoming here without her."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778926014
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family demand
OL,4,Canswers as they visit the UK for the
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,FShortly after arriving in Corby, in
OL,8,FAugust 2024, Harshita contacted
OL,9,FNorthamptonshire Police to report that
OL,10,Fshe was being abused by Lamba.
OL,12,FSonia told ITV News: "She (Harshita)
OL,13,Fwas very excited to come to the UK,
OL,14,Fand after 10 days she got a job and
OL,15,Fsaid everything was going well. But
OL,16,Fafter some time, Pankaj's behaviour
OL,17,Fwasn't good. She said he forced her to
OL,18,Fdo extra work, household work, and he
OL,19,Fwas always talk to her with abusive
OL,20,Flanguage."
OL,26,@tD@[pmtD@dpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778926014
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family demand
OL,4,Canswers as they visit the UK for the
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,FAfter contacting the police, Harshita
OL,8,Fwas referred to a refuge and moved to
OL,9,Fanother house.
OL,11,FLamba was arrested and bailed, and on
OL,12,FSeptember 5 2024, a Domestic Violence
OL,13,FProtection Notice (DVPN) and a
OL,14,FDomestic Violence Protection Order
OL,15,Fwere authorised at Northampton
OL,16,FMagistrates' Court, which remained in
OL,17,Fplace for 28 days while the
OL,18,Finvestigation continued.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778926014
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family demand
OL,4,Canswers as they visit the UK for the
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,FFour officers from Northamptonshire
OL,8,FPolice are facing misconduct hearings
OL,9,Fafter the IOPC found they have a case
OL,10,Fto answer over the way they handled
OL,11,FHarshita's domestic abuse claims.
OL,13,FTwo officers are due to face
OL,14,Fmisconduct hearings next week, on the
OL,15,Fsame day the family are set to meet
OL,16,Fofficers for an update on the case.
OL,18,FOn the night of November 10 2024,
OL,19,FHarshita apparently met with her
OL,20,Festranged husband.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778926014
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family demand
OL,4,Canswers as they visit the UK for the
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,FHer family say she had told them she
OL,8,Fwas meeting him that evening.
OL,10,FRemembering that final phone call,
OL,11,FSonia said: "She talked to my mom, and
OL,12,Fluckily that time she also spoke to my
OL,13,Fmother's mom. She was showing us the
OL,14,Fpakoras (that she'd made) and she said
OL,15,Fthat Pankaj was coming and he wanted
OL,16,Fto meet her."
OL,26,@vD@IpmvD@Ypn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778926014
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family demand
OL,4,Canswers as they visit the UK for the
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,FIt is thought that the two of them
OL,8,Fwent to the boating lake, less than a
OL,9,Fmile from her house - a place she
OL,10,Floved to visit. CCTV shows her
OL,11,Ftogether with a man thought to be
OL,12,FLamba, the last time Harshita was
OL,13,Fphotographed alive.
OL,15,FHer family contacted the police after
OL,16,Fthey didn't hear from her following
OL,17,Fthe last time they spoke, when they
OL,18,Fsaid she told them she was meeting
OL,19,Fwith Lamba.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778926014
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family demand
OL,4,Canswers as they visit the UK for the
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,FSonia said: "My father was calling
OL,8,Fher, and her phone was switched off.
OL,9,FShe never switched off her phone. We
OL,10,Fdid the same thing for two days, and
OL,11,Fthen we rang Pankaj's phone, and that
OL,12,Fwas also switched off. My father
OL,13,Ftalked to a relative and (reported her
OL,14,Fmissing).
OL,16,F"Then, after one day, we got the
OL,17,Finformation from our police station
OL,18,Fthat Harshita is no more."
OL,26,@uD@ZpmvD@Hpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778926014
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family demand
OL,4,Canswers as they visit the UK for the
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,FAfter landing in the UK, her family
OL,8,Fvisited that lake to retrace
OL,9,FHarshita's apparent final steps.
OL,11,FSatbir Singh, Harshita's father, told
OL,12,Fus: "This is the place where we saw
OL,13,Fthe last images..., so it is quite a
OL,14,Fpainful experience to come here. This
OL,15,Fis the only image... After that, we
OL,16,Fhave only heard about the dead body."
OL,26,@tD@EOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778926014
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family demand
OL,4,Canswers as they visit the UK for the
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,FSonia added: "I just feel she is here
OL,8,Fand she will come to me and say, 'how
OL,9,Fare you, sister? Nice to meet you',
OL,10,Fbut sadly she is not here, this is
OL,11,Fjust my imagination."
OL,13,FThey also wanted to see the estate
OL,14,Fwhere Harshita lived, and where police
OL,15,Fbelieve she was killed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778926014
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family demand
OL,4,Canswers as they visit the UK for the
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,FStanding near where ITV News obtained
OL,8,Fexclusive CCTV of a man pacing by his
OL,9,Fcar for hours after Lamba and Harshita
OL,10,Fare thought to have been to the lake,
OL,11,FSonia said through tears: "I am sure
OL,12,Fshe was saying 'Sonia, please, Sonia
OL,13,Fplease, save me'. I know she said it,
OL,14,FI know it."
OL,16,FWatch: CCTV footage obtained by ITV
OL,17,FNews showing a man pacing following
OL,18,FHarshita Brella's death
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778926014
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family demand
OL,4,Canswers as they visit the UK for the
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,FThe family laid flowers to remember
OL,8,Ftheir daughter, whom they
OL,9,Faffectionately called Sweetie.
OL,11,FReflecting on why they have come to
OL,12,Fthe UK, Sonia said: "I just want
OL,13,Fjustice. It is so horrible. She was so
OL,14,Fcute, so innocent."
OL,16,F"Pankaj Lamba is so cruel."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778926014
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family demand
OL,4,Canswers as they visit the UK for the
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,FHarshita's mother, Sudesh, said: "It
OL,8,Fgives me pain to see this place again.
OL,9,FI would have come with her. Now that I
OL,10,Fhave seen this place, I miss my
OL,11,Fdaughter a lot."
OL,13,FSatbir added: "As of now, we have
OL,14,Fnothing. We will only get justice when
OL,15,Fhe is arrested and brought here."
OL,17,FDetective Superintendent Johnny
OL,18,FCampbell, the Senior Investigating
OL,19,FOfficer in the case, said he looks
OL,20,Fforward to meeting with Harshita's
OL,21,Ffamily.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
