OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778926014
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family demand
OL,4,Canswers as they visit the UK for the
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,F"I was privileged to travel to India
OL,13,Flast July to meet with family members
OL,14,Fand return Harshita's personal
OL,15,Fbelongings, and I very much appreciate
OL,16,Fthe opportunity to meet with them
OL,17,Fagain," he said.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30617
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778926014
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family demand
OL,4,Canswers as they visit the UK for the
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,F"This will undoubtedly be a very
OL,8,Fdifficult and emotional visit for
OL,9,Fthem, and I hope we will be able to
OL,10,Fprovide reassurance of our absolute
OL,11,Fcommitment to achieving justice for
OL,12,FHarshita."
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30618
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778926014
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family demand
OL,4,Canswers as they visit the UK for the
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,FDetective Campbell added: "This has
OL,8,Fbeen and remains an exceptionally
OL,9,Fcomplex case. A murder investigation
OL,10,Fwas launched following Harshita's
OL,11,Fdeath in November 2024 and in March
OL,12,F2025, 24-year-old Pankaj Lamba,
OL,13,FHarshita's husband, was charged with
OL,14,Fher murder. With criminal proceedings
OL,15,Factive in the UK, we are unable to go
OL,16,Finto detail about the case.
OL,26,@oD@[OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30619
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778926014
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family demand
OL,4,Canswers as they visit the UK for the
OL,5,Cfirst time
OL,7,F"The investigation, however, is very
OL,8,Fmuch ongoing. We are continuing to
OL,9,Fwork with the appropriate agencies
OL,10,Fboth in the UK and internationally,
OL,11,Fand remain as determined as ever to
OL,12,Fsecure justice for Harshita and her
OL,13,Ffamily."
OL,15,FDuring their visit to the UK, the
OL,16,Ffamily will meet with MPs and
OL,17,FNorthamptonshire Police. More than 18
OL,18,Fmonths on from Harshita's death, they
OL,19,Fhope to leave here with answers.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/20
